Delete.

385
00:21:19,199 --> 00:21:20,199
Delete.

386
00:21:21,372 --> 00:21:22,971
Delete!

387
00:22:37,677 --> 00:22:38,773
Come to think of it,

388
00:22:38,798 --> 00:22:41,855
it's always been a one on one battle between myself and L.

389
00:22:41,880 --> 00:22:43,704
It's been going on since the beginning.

390
00:22:43,859 --> 00:22:44,926
Alright, Near.

391
00:22:44,951 --> 00:22:45,852
Fine.

392
00:22:45,877 --> 00:22:47,611
I'll come out if you come out.

393
00:22:47,636 --> 00:22:49,549
I'll accept your challenge.

